eer at the age of 15. Merritt landed her first television role as a recurring character on the ABC Family show Kyle XY. Following her television debut were a number of film roles including the female lead in the movie Wolves opposite Jason Momoa.\n\nMost well known for her role as Ophelia Pryce in The Royals on E!. Merritt has starred in a number of television shows including the Pretty Little Liars spin-off Ravenswood for ABC Family and in Crackle's The Art Of More as Olivia Brukner opposite Dennis Quaid and Kate Bosworth.\n\nIn 2018 Merritt played Cynthia Applewhite in the film Unbroken: Path to Redemption for Universal. Accepting the award for Best Supporting Actress at CIFF for her portrayal of the role.\n\nA long time fan favorite for The Hallmark Channel, Merritt has starred in eight Hallmark films. Four of these films being part of the beloved Countdown To Christmas.","name":"Merritt Patterson","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"tv_220850_keywords":{"at":1773470199540,"data":{"id":220850,"results":[{"name":"martial arts","id":779},{"name":"based on novel or book","id":818},{"name":"xianxia","id":234890},{"name":"3d animation","id":278823},{"name":"web series","id":281372},{"name":"cultivation","id":290999},{"name":"qi","id":312218},{"name":"refinement","id":312220},{"name":"donghua","id":315535},{"name":"based on web novel","id":318933}]}},"person_1639205_translations":{"at":1773470205614,"data":{"id":1639205,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Amy Morgan is a profession actress. 30 Credits. Wuthering Heights · Death Valley · Beyond Paradise · Playing Nice · We Live in Time · Steeltown Murders.","name":"Amy Morgan","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Емі Морґан","primary":false}}]}},"person_1496419_translations":{"at":1773543127953,"data":{"id":1496419,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Huang Ying (黄莺) is a Chinese voice actress.","name":"Huang Ying","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"黄莺，女，先后毕业于上海戏剧学院表演系、华东师范大学中文系。国家一级演员。上海人民广播电台文艺频率、故事频率特邀嘉宾主持人。上海电影家协会成员。\n\n她是《哈利·波特》中的“赫敏·格兰杰”（艾玛·沃森），她是《盗梦空间》中的“梅尔”（玛丽昂·歌迪亚），她是《航海王》中的“妮可·罗宾”，《魔兽世界》中的“希尔瓦娜斯”和《星际争霸2》中的虫族女王“凯瑞甘”，她也是《星际战甲》中的\"莲花\"。2016年参演电影《精灵王座》。2022年担任手游《无期迷途》配音导演，同时担任角色为澈/卡米利安/琼三位角色的配音演员。\n\n她担任译制导演、参与配音的电影、电视剧、动漫、游戏、广告、广播剧、解说等数以千计。","name":"黄莺","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"黃鶯，女，先後畢業於上海戲劇學院表演系、華東師範大學中文系。國家一級演員。上海人民廣播電台文藝頻率、故事頻率特邀嘉賓主持人。上海電影家協會成員。\n\n她是《哈利·波特》中的“赫敏·格蘭傑”（艾瑪·沃森），她是《盜夢空間》中的“梅爾”（瑪麗昂·歌迪亞），她是《海賊王》中的“妮歌·魯賓”，《魔獸世界》中的“希爾瓦娜斯”和《星際爭霸 2》中的蟲族黑枕黃鸝“凱瑞甘”，她也是《星際戰甲》中的\"蓮花\"。2016 年參演電影《精靈王座》。2022 年擔任手遊《無期迷途》配音導演，同時擔任角色為澈/卡米利安/瓊三位角色的配音演員。\n\n她擔任譯製導演、參與配音的電影、電視劇、動漫、遊戲、廣告、廣播劇、解説等數以千計。","name":"黑枕黃鸝","primary":false}}]}},"person_2674515_translations":{"at":1773599448149,"data":{"id":2674515,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lee Gi-taek","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이기택","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"李基泽","prim